\\/11\\\/manna.svg\",\"contentUrl\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipal.com\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2024\\\/11\\\/manna.svg\",\"caption\":\"Editorial Team\"},\"description\":\"Online Manipal's Editorial Team brings you informative and interesting articles on the recent developments in online education. We enable readers to gain insights into the trending online degrees, their scope &amp; benefits, and help them make informed decisions that will result in career advancement and transitions.\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipal.com\\\/blogs\\\/author\\\/online-manipal-editorial-team\"}]}<\/script>\n<!-- \/ Yoast SEO plugin. -->","yoast_head_json":{"title":"How online MA Sociology from SMU helps you in UGC NET preparation - Online Manipal","description":"MA Sociology students find UGC NET preparations easier, how does an online MA Sociology from SMU complements UGC NET exam study.","robots":{"index":"index","follow":"follow","max-snippet":"max-snippet:-1","max-image-preview":"max-image-preview:large","max-video-preview":"max-video-preview:-1"},"canonical":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3761990","og_locale":"en_GB","og_type":"article","og_title":"How online MA Sociology from SMU helps you in UGC NET preparation - Online Manipal","og_description":"MA Sociology students find UGC NET preparations easier, how does an online MA Sociology from SMU complements UGC NET exam study.","og_url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/how-online-ma-sociology-from-smu-helps-you-in-ugc-net-preparation","og_site_name":"Online Manipal","article_publisher":"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal","article_published_time":"2024-07-31T04:56:52+00:00","article_modified_time":"2025-09-03T10:18:29+00:00","og_image":[{"width":1200,"height":600,"url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/bba-mahe-direct-entry-to-phd.jpg","type":"image\/jpeg"}],"author":"Editorial Team","twitter_card":"summary_large_image","twitter_misc":{"Writte